{"tid":1838835,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"警渣為甚麼哭？ - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-01-24T07:14:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T07:55:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"75ede196bb81e50b55293ed2f2cd2208a86090bf","tid":1838835,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:14:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20200124/20849272/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200124%2F20849272%2F&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JXzUVmWcutTvqHtF1LT7nQkc%3D&h=f0624082\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200124%2F20849272%2F&h=4bed7913\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20200124/20849272/</a><br />\n<br />\n警渣為甚麼哭？ - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200124/large/1579773034_426e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200124%2Flarge%2F1579773034_426e.jpg&h=35f2c7d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n互聯網<br />\n<br />\n民間集會團隊舉辦「天下制裁」遊行，遭警方無理腰斬，其間有拒絕出示委任證的便衣警被身份不明人士打到頭破血流，竟當街無助地哭泣，畫面令人瞠目結舌。跟鏡頭前（鏡頭後更不堪設想）警渣向示威者施虐的殘暴程度相比較，這一點皮外傷算得了甚麼？入職警隊，受傷甚至送命應該早有心理準備。所以我不認為警渣是因為傷痛而哭泣。而且，即使皮肉有多痛，明知會成為200萬人的笑柄，警渣要哭，也該躲起來哭，斷斷不會當眾痛哭。<br />\n<br />\n那麼警渣為甚麼哭呢？因為委屈而哭，似乎比較符合邏輯。<br />\n<br />\n我不知道警渣為甚麼哭，但我是寫小說的人，如果我要用過去七個月來的大事件做背景，寫一個香港故事，我會這樣寫這一段：這一個警渣，因為跟上司及同事有私人恩怨，被派往前線做黑衣人，而且被命令不准出示委任證。誰都知道做這種爛頭卒，意味着甚麼，警渣含着一腔淚水，穿上黑衣、戴上口罩，到了前線。遇到另一批爛頭卒，他們早就因為互相篤背脊而積怨，結果全部被指令扮黑衣人。人多蝦人少，三個對一個，後者明知前者不能出示委任證，逼問他是不是警渣，警渣大叫「自己人」「自己人」，他們聽而不聞，亂棍扑頭。被扑頭的警渣被委屈、憤怒、恐懼吞沒，淚水決堤般湧出，在心中問自己，如果就那麼死掉了，值不值得？<br />\n<br />\n這只是小說情節而已，現實永遠比小說荒謬，警渣為甚麼哭？也許有更意想不到的理由。誰知道？ <br />\n<br />\n高慧然<br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk"},{"pid":"bc6b35eef3923b63a7e6b709426dbfeb6a4bbe1d","tid":1838835,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:15:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"badd59481e94b5b4e6761d8173580bc6e78b8684","tid":1838835,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:16:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"f92778f5beb180d65b9f6c37508732c5e97fbcc5","tid":1838835,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:50:49.000Z","msg":"佢都無見啲令仔俾人打到殘癈"},{"pid":"e28ca3362b69e464a504365fb4803536d3e0a5fb","tid":1838835,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:51:11.000Z","msg":"流兩滴血就巴巴閉"},{"pid":"515e9019648f1c059efb242477612b51cec10af8","tid":1838835,"uid":58852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:55:35.000Z","msg":"因為他知道，哭是沒有用的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}